Today CreditbureauAsia showed you an inverted hammer at the lower end of the price is a sign of reversal. If it appear at the top  it's also a reversal sign but reverse down. Usually it is call Shooting Star. CBA broke 146 resistance today to test next resistance 151. This 151 resistance was weakened today when it was breached. So we should expect more upside in the coming days with the target at the upper channel.
